WEBVTT

00:02:58.600 --> 00:03:01.376
My parents understood discrimination.

00:03:01.400 --> 00:03:04.016
My parents came from Germany.

00:03:04.040 --> 00:03:07.736
They were German Jews
who left in the 1930s,

00:03:07.760 --> 00:03:09.240
escaping the Holocaust.

00:03:09.920 --> 00:03:13.336
My parents lost family
and they lost parents.

00:03:13.360 --> 00:03:17.136
Both my parents lost
their parents in the Holocaust.

00:03:17.160 --> 00:03:19.336
And so they realized

00:03:19.360 --> 00:03:21.456
that they could not be silent

00:03:21.480 --> 00:03:24.160
as things were going wrong
for me in my life.

00:03:24.920 --> 00:03:26.296
Not me personally,

00:03:26.320 --> 00:03:28.656
but what was going on around me.

00:03:28.680 --> 00:03:31.976
They learned that because
I used a wheelchair,